001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.hilt;
002
003import dagger.Module;
004import dagger.Provides;
005import dagger.hilt.InstallIn;
006import dagger.hilt.components.SingletonComponent;
007import java.util.Random;
008
009/**
010 * Provides and returns a random secret team from selected preferences.
011 */
012@InstallIn(SingletonComponent.class)
013@Module
014public class ComponentsModule {
015
016  ComponentsModule() {
017  }
018
019  @Provides
020  Random provideRNG() {
021    return new Random();
022  }
023}
